# Walkthrough: Mobile Navigation Fix

**Date:** January 23, 2026  
**Issue:** Mobile hamburger menu not displaying items when clicked

---

## Changes Made

### 1. CSS Styles Added
**File:** [globals.css](file:///home/project/authentic-kopitiam/frontend/src/styles/globals.css#L544-L605)

Added 60 lines of mobile menu styles:
- `.mobile-menu` - Fixed positioning, flexbox layout, transform transition
- `.mobile-menu.is-open` - Transform to translateX(0) when open
- `.mobile-menu__close` - Close button styling with hover state
- `.mobile-menu__link` - Navigation links with hover/focus states

### 2. Component Refactored
**File:** [mobile-menu.tsx](file:///home/project/authentic-kopitiam/frontend/src/components/ui/mobile-menu.tsx)

| Before | After |
|--------|-------|
| Inline `style={{transform: ...}}` | CSS class `is-open` |
| `<style jsx>` block | External CSS in globals.css |
| Hash URLs (`#menu`) | Route URLs (`/menu`) |
| `<a>` tags | Next.js `<Link>` components |

